parameters: \n<Succubus>What do you want? Do you need something from Megna?

\n<Megna>Huh? A runt like you, an adventurer? You came to defeat
Megna? That's hilarious-♥

\n<Megna>You've been lured here by the request form Megna wrote! Your
little brain is so weak-♥

\n<Megna>Sniff sniff...♥ Despite being a female, you have quite a
delicious smell. Ah-, I see♥

\n<Megna>Sniff sniff...♥ Ahaha♥ Despite being a runt, you smell
pretty tasty.

\n<Megna>Do you know how a succubus eats a human? Or did you come
here without even knowing that sort of thing?

\n<Megna>Hey♥ You're getting itchy, aren't you? Is Megna's pheromone
taking effect? When humans are near a succubus, they become
like that-.

\n<Megna>Ahaa♥ Can you even fight properly in such a state? Just try
if you can? Teehee♥ Even a runt has its own way of doing
things-♥
